      "span_text": "Since the 1980s, actions to address HFI have been occurring primarily by governments, public health agencies, and non-profit organizations at the local level, despite calls from food insecurity experts, scholars and advocates for greater income support from senior governments for low-income households to prevent the establishment of HFI in the first place."
